{"search_data": "Central PMAY Affordable Rental Housing Complex (ARHC) Scheme Application / Registration FormAffordable Rental Housing Complex Scheme application & registration form, migrant workers and urban poor can apply online for ARHC scheme under Pradhan Mantri Awas Yojana (PMAY)Table of Contents  Affordable Rental Housing Complex Scheme (ARHC) Apply Online FormPMAY Affordable Rental Housing Complexes Application / RegistrationAffordable Rental Housing Complexes Scheme DetailsAffordable Rental Housing Complex Scheme (ARHC) Apply Online FormAs migrant labour and urban poor faces challenges in getting houses at an affordable rent, so the govt. will launch Affordable Rental Housing Complex Scheme 2020.PMAY Affordable Rental Housing Complexes Application / RegistrationJust like applications are invited for other housing scheme, the central govt. may invite PMAY Affordable Rental Housing Complex Scheme Apply Online Form 2020. To get houses on rent, migrant workers / urban poor will have to fill ARHC Application / Registration form. These online application forms may be invited through the MoHUA official website or through a new dedicated portal. As soon as the apply online form filling process will start, we will update it hereMinistry of Housing and Urban Affairs (MoHUA) will issue detailed guidelines for this PM Awas Yojana ARHC Scheme 2020. Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman has announced this PMAY ARHC Scheme as a component of Atmanirbhar Bharat Abhiyan (self reliant India campaign) on 14 May 2020.Affordable Rental Housing Complexes Scheme DetailsGovt. will launch this ARHC Scheme under PM Awas Yojana to ensure ease of living at affordable rent by the following measures:-Converting government funded housing in the cities (JnNURM / RAY) into Affordable Rental Housing Complexes (ARHC) under PPP mode through concessionaire.Incentivizing manufacturing units, industries, institutions, associations to develop Affordable Rental Housing Complex (ARHC) on their private land and operate.Incentivizing State Government Agencies / Central Government Organizations on the similar lines to develop Affordable Rental Housing Complexes (ARHC) and operate.Affordable Rental Housing Complexes ARHC SchemeAs the detailed information about ARHC scheme are not out yet, check the initial PMAY Affordable Rental Housing Complexes (ARHC) scheme details through the link below:- http://164.100.117.97/WriteReadData/userfiles/Aatma%20Nirbhar%20Bharat%20presentation%20Part-2%2014-5-2020.pdf  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: http://164.100.117.97/WriteReadData/userfiles/Aatma%20Nirbhar%20Bharat%20presentation%20Part-2%2014-5-2020.pdf  at  "}